text = "[b]Marble Momentum[/b]

The game is pretty simple actually. At the start of each level, you may change the different components the level has. For example in some levels you can change the slop angle,
and in some you can toggle fans on or off, or some other components. All of them allow for a lot of exciting paths that would guide the marble. 

After setting everything, press [i]Space[/i] or click the [i]Start[/i] button to roll the marble. Then just watch the marble roll and hope it lights up the switch. If not, try again with different settings.
You can press [i]R[/i] or click the [i]Reload[/i] icon at the top to restart the level at any time. After hitting the light on, next level will be loaded automatically.

You can click the [i]Home[/i] button to go back to the main menu."
